800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/patti_smith_taylor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/patti_smith_taylor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/patti_smith_taylor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/patti-smith">帕蒂·史密斯</a>最近在都柏林的舞台上引用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">折磨诗人部门</a>》中的名字——请查看下面的镜头。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="308" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454"><b>《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</b></a></li></ul><p>6 月 28 日，这位纽约朋克传奇人物在该市维卡街 (Vicar Street) 的演出场地中提到了自己与当年最成功唱片之一的主打歌的联系。</p><p>在四月份发行的这首歌中，斯威夫特特别提到了史密斯、威尔士诗人迪伦·托马斯，以及标志性的波西米亚热点曼哈顿切尔西酒店。</p><p> “<i>我当着你的面笑着说，‘你不是迪伦·托马斯，我不是帕蒂·史密斯/这不是切尔西酒店/我们是现代白痴</i>’，”她唱道，人们普遍认为这是暗指她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">1975 年</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-music-undergoes-streaming-rise-amid-reports-of-taylor-swift-romance-3443019">短暂关系</a>。</p><p>现在，史密斯已经把参考带回到了原点。正如都柏林演出的粉丝捕捉到的镜头所示，史密斯说：“好吧，我有一个小小的坦白。我不是迪伦·托马斯，但我是帕蒂·史密斯！”，引起了人群的热烈欢呼。</p><p>请参阅此处的视频：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">这不是切尔西酒店<a href="https://t.co/JFTppOsziT">pic.twitter.com/JFTppOsziT</a></p><p> — 绫<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f90d.png" alt="🤍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1fab6.png" alt="🪶" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> |风扇附件(@imaltoowell) <a href="https://twitter.com/imalltoowell/status/1809368547052879998?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 5 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>这首歌发行后不久， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/patti-smith-responds-to-taylor-swift-name-check-on-the-tortured-poets-department-3703931">史密斯在社交媒体上做出了回应，其中可以看到她正在阅读托马斯的一本诗集</a>。 “这就是说，我很高兴能在伟大的威尔士诗人迪伦·托马斯的陪伴下被提及。谢谢泰勒，”她写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C59kqTfp6lF/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rul